episodes.title: Jehovah's Witness Catch-22
episodes.description:
Jehovah's Witness Catch-22 - In this short video I discuss a catch-22 argument from the New World Translation that one can use to prove Jesus is God to the Jehovah's Witness that they encounter. The argument revolves around Revelation 22:13 and its speaker claiming to be both the Alpha & Omega, as well as the First & the Last.

Link to my new channel 'Christian Video Vault':
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtBvO5YdROe5CWU41KVde4Q

My playlist 'Proving Jesus Is God':
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0ZaautnfUXNqSSbt9EVp8amjR8xVP6v4

As a side note, I encourage my Christian brothers who are interested to examine my Playlists section here on YouTube:

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClh6ABQPVkU3N1fD7jb_6yA/playlists

I have put together a lot of good material for the believing Christian, esp. the newborn Christian, categorizing it all the best I could. There is quite a lot of good material available, ranging from apologetics, which is reasons for faith and answers to difficulties regarding faith, to Biblical teaching, to in-depth examinations of various other worldviews, as well as videos exposing satanic teachings/teachers, occultism, New World Order/Illuminati type things and many many others.

I hope the video edifies and builds up the Church of Christ. If you liked the material, feel free to subscribe to my channel for similar material in the future. I love all of you very much and I hope you're blessed in the Lord.

Godspeed,
Theophilus
